
Ranger Help for: taint
======================

SYNTAX:      taint arrow/bolt
USAGE:       forest,plains,jungle,swamp,desert
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     10 sp
SKILL TYPE:  arrow

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to use some of the native poisons in certain
terrains to poison the tips of arrows and bolts. Poisoned arrows and
bolts do increased damage over plain ones. Arrows are used in shortbows
and longbows while bolts are used in crossbows. 

